%% Sequence — Magic-link sign-in with ban-evasion gate
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant C as Sign-in form
    participant NA as Auth.js (NextAuth)
    participant SES as AWS SES
    participant CB as signIn callback
    participant BR as BannedIdentityRepository
    participant DB as Prisma adapter (MongoDB)

    U->>C: Enter email
    C->>NA: signIn('nodemailer', email)
    NA->>DB: create VerificationToken
    NA->>SES: send magic-link email
    SES-->>U: Email with one-time link
    U->>NA: Click magic link (token)
    NA->>DB: verify + consume token
    NA->>CB: signIn({ user })
    CB->>BR: findByEmailOrUserId
    alt banned
        CB-->>NA: false (deny)
        NA-->>U: Access denied
    else allowed
        CB-->>NA: true
        NA->>DB: create Session (JWT)
        NA-->>U: Authenticated session cookie
    end
